@startuml
title Sequence 06 - Self-report Status Lamaran dan Upload LoA
autonumber
actor Mahasiswa
participant "Frontend Portal\nLamaran" as FE
participant "Application API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Storage\nlocal/S3" as Storage
participant "Notification Queue" as Notif

Mahasiswa -> FE: Buka Riwayat Lamaran
FE -> API: GET /applications/my
API -> DB: Query Applications by student_id
DB --> API: Daftar lamaran + logs
API --> FE: ApplicationDetailResponse[]
FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan board status

Mahasiswa -> FE: Update status / upload LoA
alt status OFFERED diterima dengan bukti LoA
  FE -> API: POST /applications/{id}/proof
  API -> DB: Validasi application status OFFERED/ACCEPTED
  API -> Storage: Simpan file proof
  Storage --> API: proof_url
  API -> DB: Set status ACCEPTED dan insert ApplicationLogs(proof_url)
  API -> Notif: Queue notifikasi status baru
  API --> FE: Bukti berhasil diunggah
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan menunggu verifikasi CDA
else self-report status lain
  FE -> API: PATCH /applications/{id}/status
  API -> DB: Validasi transisi APPLIED -> SCREENING -> INTERVIEW -> OFFERED / WITHDRAWN
  API -> DB: Update Applications dan insert ApplicationLogs
  API --> FE: Status diperbarui
else transisi/file tidak valid
  API --> FE: 400
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan error
end
@enduml
